Name:           framerd
Version:        3.5.6
Release:        10%{?dist}
Summary:        semantic development environment

Group:          System Environment/Libraries
License:        GNU GPL
URL:            http://www.beingmeta.com/
Source0:        framerd-3.5.6.tar.gz
